STATE EX REL. JONES
v.
HAMILTON CTY. COURT OF COMMON PLEAS 2019-0638 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 24, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On respondents' motions to dismiss. Motions granted. Cause dismissed. Respondent Hudson & Marshall, L.L.C.'s motion for judgment on pleadings granted. O'Connor, C.J., and Kennedy, French, DeWine, Donnelly, and Stewart, JJ., concur. Fischer, J., not participating.
